TV star Moshe Ndiki hosted a lavish private memorial service and funeral for his dog ‘Sugar Ndiki’ on Tuesday. The ceremony was held at his home and attended by close family and friends. It was also decorated by well-known celebrity favorite décor and events company, Nono Events. In an Instagram post, Ndiki went on to thank everyone who attended and Nono Events for helping him give his "baby", Sugar, a "beautiful and amazing send off". People took to Twitter to share their views on what they described as an over-the-top funeral. 